casebody.data:
DIXIE-NET COMMUNICATIONS, INC., petitioner,
v.
BELLSOUTH TELECOMMUNICATIONS, INC., dba AT&T Mississippi, et al. No. 13-152. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013. Case below, 516 Fed.Appx. 407 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
